com.cmput301f17t07.ingroove.Model

Class HabitEvent

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.cmput301f17t07.ingroove.Model.HabitEvent
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Identifiable, java.io.Serializable

    public class HabitEvent
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable, Identifiable
    [Data Class] Abstraction of an occurrence of completing a habit All habit events have an ID and implement the Identifiable interface so that the ID can be accessed Each habit event may contain a name, comment, day, photo (optional), and location (optional)
    See Also:
    Created by Adam Otto on ####-##-##., Serialized Form
